This is your naval base. It's the first area you start on in the game and has four maps that are more or less the same as [[Phase 1/World 1|Phase 1]] 1-1 through 1-4 in the browser game.<br> It has two repair docks and is expandable up to four.<br> '''It is the only hexagon you can build ships and equipment from, as it contains your factory. If the Abyssals succeed in taking this area from you it is a GAME OVER.'''
:Fully clearing this area gives you access to [[KanColle Kai:Sandbox/Area 9|V9-1]] ('''南方連絡海域''').
